<zyHTML id="cdfe21cb-11b9-eb6b-d489-c8bb2b8cf3cf" subsection="true" caption="A character is internally stored as a number">
<h3>A character is internally stored as a number</h3>
</zyHTML>


<zyHTML id="84367031-9187-4e1f-870d-23f83f6465c1">
<p> Under the hood, a char variable stores a number. Ex:  'a' is stored as 97.  In an output statement, the  compiler outputs the number's corresponding character. </p> 
</zyHTML>



